title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 6: Tinder, Troubled Islanders & More
description:
In this week's episode, the boys were all over the road. They discuss the recent spate of injuries to star players, the troubled Islanders, and puck line vs. money line. RA, Ryan, and Mike discuss modern dating and the differences between Tinder and actually having a conversation with a woman in person. Then they answer #AllRightHamilton questions before finishing things up with the wildly popular #AskAMillennial segment. This was a fun episode.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
